bookmark_border
On this page
Daily video metadata (version 1.2)
Daily video metadata (version 1.3)

This report is a complete list of all videos uploaded to this account and includes each video's attributes and settings.



Daily video metadata (version 1.2)

This report summarizes the daily metadata for videos. The report may contain multiple rows per video.

The reportType id for this report is content_owner_video_metadata_a2.

Contents
Primary Key:
video_id
channel_id
claim_id
channel_display_name
asset_id
custom_id
third_party_video_id

Additional fields:
video_length
views
comments
effective_policy
video_privacy_status
video_url
category
embedding_allowed
